    public class Run
extends java.util.ArrayList<RunLine>
    This class is a retrieval run. Each Run class is made of a list of RunLine.

      • computeRanks

        public void computeRanks()
        This method re-computes the Run. It sort all the RunLines in the instance in a decreasing order and then set RunLine ranks following items order (from the major score to the minor one).

      • printInfo

        public void printInfo()
        This method is useful for debug purposes. It prints to command line some Run instance information. The output string gives the name and the size (the number of RunLine elements) of the instance.

        public void normalize()
        Perform Run normalization using minimum and maximum score values
